RMCS Messages to support Ardumower Control Center

RMCS Messages (NMEA like sentences) added for serial console output and commands. Common commands still works when use RMCS.

To enable RMCS, set rmcsUse to true in mower.cpp

RMC Message for GPS added

add RMCS Message fpr GPS data (lat/lon)

Bug fix serial command read

By using Console.readString, the mower can get stuck and act like a zombie. The reason is, readSerial is a blocking function with a default timeout of 1000ms. If new data arrive faster, it will never return. Also if setting timeout lower by using setTimeout function, it will fail if many messages arrive.
Therefore I changed back to waitStringConsole as it takes many messages per second without any trouble.
Other changes: optional CONSOLE_BAUDRATE when using CC and DUE (must be uncommented to use)
